data.description: Welcome home to your rural retreat! Situated on a sprawling 1.78-acre lot, this property offers the perfect blend of updated living and ample space for your hobbies or storage needs.There are 2 outbuildings on the property: a heated 30x40 garage, ideal for car enthusiasts or extra storage, and a spacious 40x70 heated shop, perfect for larger projects or farm equipment. Inside the main house, enjoy an open floor plan with plenty of natural light in the living room and a well-appointed kitchen with stainless steel appliances.The 4 bedrooms are generously sized, and the bathrooms have been tastefully updated. Located in a peaceful rural neighborhood yet close to amenities, this property provides the serenity you desire. Don't miss the chance to make this your new home. Schedule your showing today. The 40x70 outbuilding was just just updated with new insulation, drywall, lights, garage doors, exterior paint, and a wood-burning stove for those chilly days.
